Exhaling Dust.title: Exhaling Dust
Exhaling Dust.description: A 3D puzzle and space exploration game with physical puzzles and narrative elements.

Abbott Internship.title: Abbott Internship
Abbott Internship.description: The projects I worked on during my time as an intern at Abbott.

Ocean Cleanup.title: Ocean Cleanup
Ocean Cleanup.description: A low-poly 3D ocean exploration and cleanup game made for the Progression Mechanics Game Jam.

CatSAT.title: CatSAT
CatSAT.description: A SAT solver developed by Dr. Ian Horswill that uses an optimized WalkSAT algorithm to solve constraint problems and pseudoboolean constraint problems.

Smart Context Stories.title: Smart Context Stories
Smart Context Stories.organization: COMP_SCI 338-0: Practicum in Intelligent Information Systems
Smart Context Stories.description: An AI Chrome extension that catches you up on the news you missed while you were busy.

ZenDog.title: ZenDog
ZenDog.description: A webapp allowing dog owners to connect with experts and receive curated content.

DiningInformant.title: DiningInformant
DiningInformant.description: A webapp that allows Northwestern students to see wait times and menus for on-campus dining halls.

When the Devil Takes Hold.title: When the Devil Takes Hold
When the Devil Takes Hold.description: A 2D pixel puzzle game where you solve murderous puzzles to appease a demon, all while trying to escape his wrath.

Riverswood Manor.title: Riverswood Manor
Riverswood Manor.description: A 3D escape room game where you play as a butler trying to escape a haunted mansion.

We Three Witches.title: We Three Witches
We Three Witches.description: A 2D pixel platformer game where you play as one of three witches fighting AI enemy monsters.

Papa's What-Is-Going-On-Eria.title: Papa's What-Is-Going-On-Eria
Papa's What-Is-Going-On-Eria.description: A cooking flash game where you fulfill restaurant orders as ingredients gradually become corrupted and unusable.

SonglyBot.title: SonglyBot
SonglyBot.description: A Discord bot created for the official Overture Games Discord server. Features are developed to make the server more interactive and fun.

Intervallic.title: Intervallic
Intervallic.description: A video game where you can use your instrument to control an alien robot cat as it navigates the world through music.

Imaginarium.title: Imaginarium
Imaginarium.description: A language developed by Dr. Ian Horswill to generate just about anything you could imagine.

Polygonal Folding.title: Polygonal Folding
